oft"},["P",{"class":"font-inter text-sm leading-relaxed text-steel-grey"},"Illustrative surface-treatment diagram. Actual results depend on the surface, application, testing conditions, contamination, and maintenance."]]],["DIV",{"class":"min-w-0 max-w-full ","style":"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)"},["DIV",{"class":"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4"},["DIV",{"class":"surface-card p-6"},["svg",{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":"24","height":"24","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","stroke-width":"2","stroke-linecap":"round","stroke-linejoin":"round","class":"lucide lucide-droplets w-8 h-8 text-accent mb-4","aria-hidden":"true"},["path",{"d":"M7 16.3c2.2 0 4-1.83 4-4.05 0-1.16-.57-2.26-1.71-3.19S7.29 6.75 7 5.3c-.29 1.45-1.14 2.84-2.29 3.76S3 11.1 3 12.25c0 2.22 1.8 4.05 4 4.05z"}],["path",{"d":"M12.56 6.6A10.97 10.97 0 0 0 14 3.02c.5 2.5 2 4.9 4 6.5s3 3.5 3 5.5a6.98 6.98 0 0 1-11.91 4.97"}]],["H3",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-ink mb-3"},"Untreated surface"],["P",{"class":"font-inter text-steel-grey text-sm leading-relaxed"},"Liquid contamination remains between the floor and footwear."]],["DIV",{"class":"surface-card p-6 border-accent/20"},["svg",{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":"24","height":"24","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","stroke-width":"2","stroke-linecap":"round","stroke-linejoin":"round","class":"lucide lucide-footprints w-8 h-8 text-accent mb-4","aria-hidden":"true"},["path",{"d":"M4 16v-2.38C4 11.5 2.97 10.5 3 8c.03-2.72 1.49-6 4.5-6C9.37 2 10 3.8 10 5.5c0 3.11-2 5.66-2 8.68V16a2 2 0 1 1-4 0Z"}],["path",{"d":"M20 20v-2.38c0-2.12 1.03-3.12 1-5.62-.03-2.72-1.49-6-4.5-6C14.63 6 14 7.8 14 9.5c0 3.11 2 5.66 2 8.68V20a2 2 0 1 0 4 0Z"}],["path",{"d":"M16 17h4"}],["path",{"d":"M4 13h4"}]],["H3",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-ink mb-3"},"Treated surface"],["P",{"class":"font-inter text-steel-grey text-sm leading-relaxed"},"Microscopic channels help disperse contamination and imp