"},["svg",{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":"24","height":"24","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","stroke-width":"2","stroke-linecap":"round","stroke-linejoin":"round","class":"lucide lucide-circle-check-big w-4 h-4 text-accent mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0","aria-hidden":"true"},["path",{"d":"M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"}],["path",{"d":"m9 11 3 3L22 4"}]],["SPAN",{"class":"font-inter text-steel-grey text-sm"},"Other compatible mineral surfaces following testing"]]],["DIV",{"class":"rounded-2xl border p-5 border-amber-200 bg-amber-50"},["P",{"class":"font-inter text-sm leading-relaxed text-steel-grey"},"Surface composition, finish, sealants, previous coatings, and condition can affect results. A test area must be completed before full application."]]],["DIV",{},["H2",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-3xl text-ink mb-6"},"Performance and Testing"],["P",{"class":"font-inter text-steel-grey leading-relaxed mb-5"},"Performance must be reviewed against the applicable surface, test area, maintenance conditions, and supporting technical documentation."],["DIV",{"class":"rounded-2xl border p-5 border-accent/20 bg-accent-soft"},["P",{"class":"font-inter text-sm leading-relaxed text-steel-grey"},"Performance figures are surface- and test-specific. Supporting technical documentation should be reviewed for the applicable use case."]]]]]],["SECTION",{"class":"section-pad bg-white"},["DIV",{"class":"max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full min-w-0 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 "},["DIV",{"class":"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10"},["DIV",{},["H2",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-3xl text-ink mb-5"},"Surface Appearance and Test Area"],["DIV",{"class":"rounded-2xl border p-5 border-amber-200 bg-amber-50"},["P",{"class":"font-inter text-sm leading-relaxed text-steel-grey"},"Treatment may cause temporary whitening or efflorescence that normally reduces over time. A slight dulling effect may occur on some surfaces. A test area is completed before full application to identify any potential change in appearance."]]],["DIV",{},["H2",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-3xl text-ink mb-5"},"Maintenance and Rejuvenation"],["P",{"class":"font-inter text-steel-grey leading-relaxed"},"Routine cleaning does not always prevent the gradual buildup of film and residue from cleaning products. When buildup reduces traction, the surface may require CRS™ cleaning and rejuvenation. Most commercial applications may require assessment or rejuvenation within approximately one to three years, depending on traffic, contamination, surface condition, and maintenance practices."]]],["DIV",{"class":"mt-10"},["DIV",{"class":"grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4"},["DIV",{"class":"relative surface-card p-5"},["SPAN",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-4xl text-accent/20"},"01"],["P",{"class":"font-sora font-semibold text-ink mt-3"},"Initial surface assessment"]],["DIV",{"class":"relative surface-card p-5"},["SPAN",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-4xl text-accent/20"},"02"],["P",{"class":"font-sora font-semibold text-ink mt-3"},"Test-area application"]],["DIV",{"class":"relative surface-card p-5"},["SPAN",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-4xl text-accent/20"},"03"],["P",{"class":"font-sora font-semibold text-ink mt-3"},"Safe Solution® treatment"]],["DIV",{"class":"relative surface-card p-5"},["SPAN",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-4xl text-accent/20"},"04"],["P",{"class":"font-sora font-semibold text-ink mt-3"},"Daily or routine Clean Step™ maintenance"]],["DIV",{"class":"relative surface-card p-5"},["SPAN",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-4xl text-accent/20"},"05"],["P",{"class":"font-sora font-semibold text-ink mt-3"},"Scheduled written inspection"]],["DIV",{"class":"relative surface-card p-5"},["SPAN",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-4xl text-accent/20"},"06"],["P",{"class":"font-sora font-semibold text-ink mt-3"},"CRS™ rejuvenation when required"]]]]]],["SECTION",{"class":"section-pad bg-surface-soft"},["DIV",{"class":"max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full min-w-0 px-