the surface, application, site conditions, maintenance, jurisdiction, and supporting documentation. A test-area assessment is required before full application."]]],["SECTION",{"class":"section-pad bg-white"},["DIV",{"class":"max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full min-w-0 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 "},["DIV",{"class":"flex flex-col text-center items-center mb-10","style":"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)"},["SPAN",{"class":"inline-block font-inter text-[11px] sm:text-xs tracking-[0.22em] uppercase font-semibold mb-3 text-accent"},"Clean Step™ Multi-Purpose Cleaner"],["H2",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight max-w-3xl mx-auto text-ink"},"Superior Low-Residue Cleaning for ",["SPAN",{"class":"gradient-text"},"Safer Floors"]],["P",{"class":"mt-4 text-base md:text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed text-steel-grey mx-auto"},"Clean Step™ supports ongoing floor appearance, cleanliness, and safety as part of the complete program."],["DIV",{"class":"mt-5 flex gap-2 items-center"},["DIV",{"class":"h-px w-10 bg-accent/40"}],["DIV",{"class":"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"}],["DIV",{"class":"h-px w-10 bg-accent/40"}]]],["DIV",{"class":"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5"},["DIV",{"class":"surface-card p-6"},["H3",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-ink text-xl mb-3"},"Super Low-Residue Formula"],["P",{"class":"font-inter text-steel-grey text-sm leading-relaxed"},"Many commercial cleaners can leave residue that attracts and holds dirt, affecting appearance and traction. Clean Step™ is designed as a highly effective, low-residue cleaner to support cleaner and safer floor surfaces."]],["DIV",{"class":"surface-card p-6"},["H3",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-ink text-xl mb-3"},"Optimal pH-Neutral Strength"],["P",{"class":"font-inter text-steel-grey text-sm leading-relaxed"},"Safe Solution® treated floors should be maintained using a high-quality, user-friendly cleaner that does not leave significant residue. Clean Step™ is designed to support the ongoing floor-safety program."]],["DIV",{"class":"surface-card p-6"},["H3",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-ink text-xl mb-3"},"Commercial Cost Efficiency"],["P",{"class":"font-inter text-steel-grey text-sm leading-relaxed"},"Regular use of one versatile commercial cleaner may reduce the need to stock multiple specialized products. Commercial and distributor pricing can be provided through an approved quotation."]]]]],["SECTION",{"class":"section-pad bg-surface-soft"},["DIV",{"class":"max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full min-w-0 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 "},["DIV",{"class":"flex flex-col text-center items-center mb-10","style":"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)"},["SPAN",{"class":"inline-block font-inter text-[11px] sm:text-xs tracking-[0.22em] uppercase font-semibold mb-3 text-accent"},"Floor Care Safety Program"],["H2",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight max-w-3xl mx-auto text-ink"},"The Benefits of a Structured Program ",["SPAN",{"class":"gradient-text"},"Without Unnecessary Lock-In"]],["P",{"class":"mt-4 text-base md:text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed text-steel-grey mx-auto"},"The Floor Care Safety Program combines treatment, approved cleaning, scheduled inspections, written documentation, and CRS™ rejuvenation to help commercial floors remain at maximum effectiveness."],["DIV",{"class":"mt-5 flex gap-2 items-center"},["DIV",{"class":"h-px w-10 bg-accent/40"}],["DIV",{"class":"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"}],["DIV",{"class":"h-px w-10 bg-accent/40"}]]],["DIV",{"class":"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5"},["DIV",{"class":"surface-card p-6"},["H3",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-ink text-lg mb-3"},"Clear Commercial Terms"],["P",{"class":"font-inter text-steel-grey text-sm leading-relaxed"},"Program scope, cancellation, renewal, service intervals, and customer responsibilities should be confirmed in the customer agreement."]],["DIV",{"class":"surface-card p-6"},["H3",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-ink text-lg mb-3"},"Scheduled Inspection and Rejuvenation"],["P",{"class":"font-inter text-steel-grey text-sm leading-relaxed"},"Commercial protection and maintenance intervals vary. Scheduled inspections help determine whether cleaning, maintenance, or CRS™ rejuvenation is required."]],["DIV",{"class":"surface-card p-6"},["H3",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-ink text-lg mb-3"},"Annual Program Option"],["P",{"class":"font-inter text-steel-grey text-sm leading-relaxed"},"Where available, customers may select an annual inspection and rejuvenation program for maximum floor-care consistency."]],["DIV",{"class":"surface-card p-6"},["H3",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-ink text-lg mb-3"},"Complete Floor-Safety Support"],["P",{"class":"font-inter text-steel-grey text-sm leading-relaxed"},"The program may include written inspections, Safe Solution® treatment, Clean Step™ maintenance cleaner, scheduled CRS™ rejuvenation, maintenance guidance, commercial pricing, and follow-up documentation."]]]]],["SECTION",{"class":"py-12 sm:py-16 bg-white"},["DIV",{"class":"max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full min-w-0 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 "},["DIV",{"class":"flex flex-col text-center items-center mb-10","style":"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)"},["SPAN",{"class":"inline-block font-inter text-[11px] sm:text-xs tracking-[0.22em] uppercase font-semibold mb-3 text-accent"},"Target Industries"],["H2",{"class":"font-sora font-bold text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight max-w-3xl mx-auto text-ink"},"Where Floor-Safety Programs ",["SPAN",{"class":"gradient-text"},"Fit Best"]],["P",{"class":"mt-4 text-base md:text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed text-steel-grey mx-auto"},"Safe Solution® is relevant to sites where hard surfaces, traffic, maintenance, and documentation can affect operational safety."],["DIV",{"class":"mt-5 flex gap-2 items-center"},["DIV",{"class":"h-px w-10 bg-accent/40"}],["DIV",{"class":"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"}],["DIV",{"class":"h-px w-10 bg-accent/40"}]]],["DIV",{"class":"grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-c